04:08.608 --> 04:11.210
This is excellent
work, very thorough.

04:11.244 --> 04:12.311
Lovely.

04:12.345 --> 04:14.246
Makes me want
to poke my eyes out.

04:14.281 --> 04:15.581
You may hate it,

04:15.615 --> 04:17.116
but it is amazing.

04:17.149 --> 04:19.819
Let's hope
it worth it.

04:46.546 --> 04:47.746
Nobody followed you?
No, don't worry.

04:47.781 --> 04:49.014
I doubled back, like, five times

04:49.049 --> 04:50.916
to make sure no one tailed me.

04:50.951 --> 04:53.352
Where do I
deliver the body?

04:53.386 --> 04:55.788
Back entrance to the Jackson,
uh, Arboretum, all right?

04:55.822 --> 04:58.224
There's no night security
there since the sequester.

04:58.258 --> 04:59.358
What's my window?

04:59.392 --> 05:01.293
Five hours all in.

05:01.328 --> 05:05.264
I know you don't like this idea.
Yeah.

05:05.298 --> 05:07.900
You've been hunting Pelant
for months on your own.

05:07.934 --> 05:09.094
Yeah, and I've gotten
nowhere,

05:09.102 --> 05:10.369
so I got to try
something new here.

05:10.403 --> 05:11.570
But you don't like it.

05:11.605 --> 05:12.738
Yeah, I don't like it.

05:15.609 --> 05:17.543
Pelant put me

05:17.577 --> 05:20.479
behind a desk
for the rest of my career.

05:20.514 --> 05:21.947
I appreciate you giving me
this chance

05:21.982 --> 05:24.717
to catch the bastard.

05:28.388 --> 05:31.123
Wow, that's-- wow.

05:31.158 --> 05:33.125
It was actually a
fascinating exercise.

05:33.160 --> 05:37.563
Do you know this is the first
time I've burned a human bone?

05:37.597 --> 05:38.764
Not the right tone, Bones.

05:38.798 --> 05:40.299
- Oh, yeah.
- So, the body

05:40.333 --> 05:41.767
has to be displayed
on this big boulder

05:41.801 --> 05:44.637
at the entrance to
the fern grotto.

05:44.671 --> 05:47.206
According to the myth,
Prometheus' torment began

05:47.240 --> 05:49.108
each day with
the rising sun,

05:49.142 --> 05:51.277
so the skull needs
to face the east.

05:51.311 --> 05:52.545
You got it.

05:52.579 --> 05:54.680
Presentation is vital. Deviate
even slightly, and Pelant will know

05:54.714 --> 05:56.782
we're setting him up.
All right.

05:56.816 --> 05:58.217
Well, I'm not about
to argue with a woman

05:58.251 --> 05:59.451
who can solve a murder

05:59.486 --> 06:01.086
using only a tooth
and a magnifying glass.

06:01.121 --> 06:04.456
I have solved a murder
using only a tooth,

06:04.491 --> 06:07.860
but I used significantly
more sophisticated equipment

06:07.894 --> 06:09.361
than a magnifying glass.

06:09.396 --> 06:10.930
I'll do it exactly
the way you said.

06:10.964 --> 06:13.098
Well, Flynn's motivated,
he'll get it done.

06:14.901 --> 06:17.036
Five hours, Flynn.

06:22.342 --> 06:23.742
I won't forget this, Booth.

06:23.777 --> 06:25.778
You're doing me a big favor.

06:33.653 --> 06:35.821
Do you wish
you were going with him?

06:35.855 --> 06:38.991
I wish I'd killed Pelant
three months ago.

06:39.025 --> 06:41.760
It'd be better
to catch him alive.

06:41.795 --> 06:43.896
Better for who?

06:53.340 --> 06:56.842
I wish the call
would come in.

06:56.876 --> 06:58.244
We could have sex.
Huh?

06:58.278 --> 06:59.678
Well, our bodies need
to relieve tension

06:59.713 --> 07:00.913
so we can sleep.

07:00.947 --> 07:02.248
Oh, way to take
the romance out of it.

07:02.282 --> 07:03.916
Well, I'm just
being practical.

07:03.950 --> 07:07.586
I just know I always sleep
best after several orgasms.

07:07.621 --> 07:10.055
Okay, what, is that
some kind of a challenge?

07:10.090 --> 07:12.658
Maybe.

07:17.564 --> 07:18.931
Flynn?

07:18.965 --> 07:19.932
No, FBI.

07:19.966 --> 07:21.333
They found the body.

07:33.113 --> 07:35.047
- Police responded to a call...
- Okay, so what do we got?

07:35.081 --> 07:38.817
The remains were found by
a dog walker one hour ago.

07:38.852 --> 07:40.519
She called it
in to Metro.

07:40.553 --> 07:41.520
Poor woman will have
nightmares

07:41.554 --> 07:43.122
for the rest
of her life.

07:43.156 --> 07:44.790
Well, we can't fake
everything. Time of death?

07:44.824 --> 07:47.426
Blowfly larvae indicate
ten hours ago.

07:47.460 --> 07:49.395
The extent of the evisceration

07:49.429 --> 07:50.696
and the manner

07:50.730 --> 07:52.698
in which the body
is bound indicate

07:52.732 --> 07:53.999
a retelling
of the Prometh...

07:54.034 --> 07:56.969
Oh, God.

07:57.003 --> 07:58.437
A flower.

07:58.471 --> 08:01.240
It's not us?

08:01.274 --> 08:02.408
Oh, no.

08:02.442 --> 08:04.209
Hodgins, do you know?

08:04.244 --> 08:06.979
Yeah, it's, it's a monkshood.

08:07.013 --> 08:08.981
Means "A foe is near."

08:09.015 --> 08:10.783
This is a message
from Pelant.

08:10.817 --> 08:11.917
He's telling us
we didn't fool him.

08:11.951 --> 08:13.118
It's worse than that.

08:13.153 --> 08:16.388
What?
This isn't our body.

08:16.423 --> 08:17.656
What?
Are you sure?

08:17.691 --> 08:20.159
This victim
has remodeled fractures

08:20.193 --> 08:22.861
on the third and fourth
left ribs and both clavicles.

08:22.896 --> 08:24.997
Come on, come on, come on.

08:25.031 --> 08:27.466
This remodeling wasn't
in our corpse.

08:27.500 --> 08:31.036
It suggests bullet wounds
that are less than a year old.

08:31.071 --> 08:33.205
It's Flynn.
Well, how do you know?

08:33.239 --> 08:35.374
He took those bullets for me.
I know those wounds.

08:35.408 --> 08:36.842
Hi, this is Flynn.

08:36.876 --> 08:38.811
If you're listening to this
instead of talking to me,

08:38.845 --> 08:41.080
I must have
a really good reason.

